SIGNATURES Pursuant to the requirements of the Securities Exchange Act of 1934, the registrant has duly caused this report to be signed on its behalf by the undersigned hereunto duly authorized. BECTON, DICKINSON AND COMPANY (Registrant) By: /s/ Dean J. Paranicas ----------------------- Dean J. Paranicas Vice President, Corporate Secretary and Public Policy Date: July 22, 2004 2
