BD BOARD DECLARES DIVIDEND
Franklin Lakes, NJ (May 24, 2005)
The Board of Directors of BD (Becton, Dickinson and Company) (NYSE:BDX) has declared a quarterly dividend of 18 cents per common share. The dividend will be payable on June 30, 2005 to holders of record on June 9, 2005. The indicated annual dividend rate is 72 cents per share.
