BD BOARD DECLARES DIVIDEND
 
 
Franklin Lakes, NJ (November 21, 2006)
 The Board of Directors of BD (Becton, Dickinson and Company) (NYSE:BDX) has declared a quarterly dividend of 24.5 cents per common share, an increase of 3 cents per share, or approximately 14%, from the previous quarter. The dividend will be payable on January 2, 2007 to holders of record on December 12, 2006. At the current rate, the annual dividend for fiscal 2007 would be 98 cents per share, a rise of approximately 14% from a year ago.
 
