, at 10:00 a.m. (ET) Wednesday, April 25, 2007. The conference call will be available for replay on BD's website,
www.bd.com/investors
, or at 1-866-373-9238 (domestic) and 1-203-369-0284 (international) through the close of business on Wednesday, May 2, 2007.
