           Becton, Dickinson and Company ("BD") has elected John R. Considine as Vice Chairman and Chief Financial Officer of BD, and a member of the Board of Directors, effective March 18, 2008. A copy of the press release issued by BD in connection with Mr. Considine's election is attached hereto as Exhibit 99.1.
 
