     3. The statements made in each of the Pricing Disclosure Package and the Prospectus under the captions "Description of Debt Securities" and "Description of Notes" (including, in the case of the Pricing Disclosure Package, the information set forth in the Free Writing Prospectus) insofar as they purport to constitute summaries of certain terms of documents referred to therein, constitute accurate summaries of the terms of such documents in all material respects.
